               <code code="51727-6" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="INACTIVE INGREDIENT SECTION"/>
               <title>INACTIVE INGREDIENTS:</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Water, Glycerin, Polysorbate 20, Propylene Glycol, Lactic Acid, Avena Sativa (Oat) Kernel Extract, Ceramide EOP, Ceramide AP, Ceramide NP, Fragrance, Potassium Sorbate, Methylisothiazolinone, Sodium Lauroyl Lactylate.</paragraph>
